[3.008345, "o", "+------------------------------------------------------+\r\r\n| ai_sast interactive terminal                         |\r\r\n+------------------------------------------------------+\r\r\n| Camran Shahvali                                      |\r\r\n| GitHub: https://github.com/CamranShahvali            |\r\r\n| LinkedIn: https://linkedin.com/in/camran-shahvali-9409b61a6 |\r\r\n+------------------------------------------------------+\r\r\nEngine: Ready\r\r\nGateway: Connected\r\r\nModel: deepseek-coder:6.7b\r\r\n\r\r\n\r\r\n1. Scan repository\r\r\n2. Scan single C++ file\r\r\n3. Scan with engine only (choose target)\r\r\n4. Scan with engine + LLM review (choose target)\r\r\n5. Run demo case\r\r\n6. Setup & tutorials\r\r\n7. Exit\r\r\nSelect an option [1-7]: "]
[9.171066, "o", "6\r\r\n\r\r\nSetup & tutorials\r\r\n-----------------\r\r\nEngine-only mode\r\r\n  Use deterministic scanning when you want the engine to remain the only source of truth.\r\r\n  Example:\r\r\n    ./build/sast-cli scan --repo tests/cases/demo --format text\r\r\n\r\r\n  Safer first interactive runs:\r\r\n    - Curated five-outcome demo\r\r\n    - Mixed single-file demo at tests/demo/mixed_case\r\r\n\r\r\nConnecting local AI with Ollama\r\r\n  1. Start Ollama locally.\r\r\n  2. Pull a local model if you do not already have one.\r\r\n  3. Start llm_gateway and point it at your local Ollama endpoint.\r\r\n\r\r\nRecommended models\r\r\n  - Start with deepseek-coder:6.7b (the current repo default).\r\r\n  - If you try alternatives, prefer code-focused local models that can follow strict JSON output reliably.\r\r\n\r\r\nStarting the gateway\r\r\n  source .venv/bin/activate\r\r\n  export SAST_LLM_ENABLED=1\r\r\n  export SAST_LLM_PROVIDER=ollama\r\r\n  export SAST_LLM_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:11434\r\r\n  export SAST_LLM_MODEL=deepseek-coder:6.7b\r\r\n  uvicorn llm_gateway.app.main:app --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8081\r\r\n\r\r\nTroubleshooting LLM detection\r\r\n  - If Gateway shows 'Not detected', make sure llm_gateway is running on http://127.0.0.1:8081.\r\r\n  - Check: curl http://127.0.0.1:8081/health\r\r\n  - If the gateway is up but the model is wrong, verify SAST_LLM_MODEL in the gateway shell.\r\r\n  - If scans hang, test the engine-only path first and then bring the gateway back.\r\r\n\r\r\nPress Enter to return to the menu..."]
