[44.355499, "o", "tests/demo/mixed_case\r\r\n\r\r\nai_sast 0.2.0\r\r\nmode: validated_scan\r\r\nphilosophy: candidate -> validate -> prove vulnerable or dismiss\r\r\ncompilation_database: /home/kingc/projects/demo/synthetic\r\r\nfindings: 3\r\r\n\r\r\n[confirmed_issue] command_injection.system\r\r\n  location: /home/kingc/projects/demo/tests/demo/mixed_case/mixed_paths.cpp:7\r\r\n  deterministic:\r\r\n    confidence: 0.94 deterministic=true\r\r\n    source: command\r\r\n    sink:   system(command)\r\r\n    explanation: positive vulnerability conditions were satisfied without a safety barrier\r\r\n\r\r\n[safe_suppressed] path_traversal.file_open\r\r\n  location: /home/kingc/projects/demo/tests/demo/mixed_case/mixed_paths.cpp:29\r\r\n  deterministic:\r\r\n    confidence: 0.98 deterministic=true\r\r\n    source: canonicalize_under_root(argv[2], \"/srv/demo-root\")\r\r\n    sink:   fopen(safe_path.c_str(), \"r\")\r\r\n    explanation: canonicalized path is confined under a fixed root\r\r\n    safe_reasoning: canonicalized path is confined under a fixed root\r\r\n\r\r\n[needs_review] dangerous_string.unbounded_copy\r\r\n  location: /home/kingc/projects/demo/tests/demo/mixed_case/mixed_paths.cpp:35\r\r\n  deterministic:\r\r\n    confidence: 0.58 deterministic=false\r\r\n    source: argv[3]\r\r\n    sink:   memcpy(scratch, argv[3], length)\r\r\n    explanation: copy bound expression could not be proven against the destination extent\r\r\n    ambiguous_reasoning: copy bound expression could not be proven against the destination extent\r\r\n  llm_review:\r\r\n    provider_status: ok\r\r\n    judgment: needs_review confidence=0.58\r\r\n    reasoning: Deterministic judgment remains needs_review because the compact context could not be proven safe and requires review. Safety of the bound is not established.\r\r\n    remediation: Check the runtime length against the destination extent before the memcpy-style sink, or tie the bound directly to sizeof(destination).\r\r\n\r\r\n\r\r\n\r\r\n\r\r\n1. Scan repository\r\r\n2. Scan single C++ file\r\r\n3. Scan with engine only (choose target)\r\r\n4. Scan with engine + LLM review (choose target)\r\r\n5. Run demo case\r\r\n6. Setup & tutorials\r\r\n7. Exit\r\r\nSelect an option [1-7]: "]
